comments: Suggs (ORL) brings his forearm slightly forward and marginal contact occurs with Powell (LAC) as he releases his pass.
George (LAC) establishes the ball in the frontcourt prior to eight seconds passing after Los Angeles had gained possession in the backcourt.
Ingles (ORL) and Harden (LAC) come together off-ball and marginal contact occurs as the two players disengage.
M. Wagner (ORL) is positioned inside of the restricted area when body contact occurs with George (LAC) and the play should be deemed a shooting foul.
Harden (LAC) brings his left hand forward and incidental hand on ball contact occurs with Banchero (ORL), which legally dislodges the ball from his grasp.
Harden (LAC) moves alongside Banchero's (ORL) path and Harden absorbs the marginal contact with the offensive player after his gather into the driving shot attempt.
Powell (LAC) and Ingles (ORL) move together off-ball and marginal contact occurs as Powell attempts to disengage to set the pick.
Banchero (ORL) brings his right hand toward the ball and makes clean contact with it, which legally deflects the ball away from Leonard (LAC) during his dribble drive.
After Banchero (ORL) deflects the ball, Leonard's (LAC) fingertips make last contact with the ball prior to it bouncing out of bounds. Possession should have been awarded to Orlando.
Isaac (ORL) and George (LAC) come together during the screen and marginal contact occurs as the two players disengage.
Isaac (ORL) makes clean contact with the ball and legally dislodges it during George's (LAC) driving shot attempt.

M. Wagner (ORL) firms up in George's (LAC) path and absorbs the marginal body contact with George during the driving shot attempt in the paint. After Isaac's (ORL) clean block, M. Wagner's left arm comes down and incidental arm contact occurs.
Harden (LAC) brings his left hand to the ball and cleanly dislodges it from Banchero's (ORL) grasp at the end of his drive.
Suggs (ORL) brings his arm down and avoids making contact with Leonard's (LAC) arm during his jump shot attempt.
Banchero (ORL) and Leonard (LAC) come together during the inbound and marginal contact occurs as Banchero releases away from the defender.
Suggs (ORL) raises his right hand up and brushes the ball as Harden (LAC) releases his pass.

Ingles (ORL) reaches in for the ball and makes contact with George's (LAC) right wrist, causing him to lose control of the ball out of bounds. Although the illegal contact causes the ball to go out of bounds, possession should have been awarded to Orlando.
Isaac (ORL) avoids making illegal contact with George (LAC) during his contest of the jump shot attempt.
Leonard (LAC) briefly rests his hands on F. Wagner's (ORL) sides and the marginal contact dissolves as the screen is set.
Leonard's (LAC) hand brushes F. Wagner's (ORL) back as he retrieves the inbound pass and the contact is marginal.
George (LAC) makes last contact with the ball prior to it falling out of bounds. Possession is properly awarded to Orlando.
M. Wagner's (ORL) arms come out slightly as he attempts to firm up in Leonard's (LAC) path and marginal contact occurs during the screen.
F. Wagner (ORL) splits his feet in the air after releasing the jump shot attempt and marginal lower body contact occurs with Leonard (LAC) as he returns to the floor.
